  <li>
<a href="https://studentprivacy.ed.gov/sites/default/files/resource_document/file/FERPA%20and%20Coronavirus%20Frequently%20Asked%20Questions.pdf">Protecting Student Privacy: FERPA and the Coronavirus</a>  (<a href="https://studentprivacy.ed.gov/resources/ferpa-and-coronavirus-disease-2019-covid-19-spanish">Español</a>)  (March 12, 2020)</li>
