  <li>
<strong><a href="https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/community/schools-childcare/guidance-for-schools.html">CDC Interim Guidance for Administrators of US K-12 Schools and Childcare Programs: </a></strong>Plan, Prepare, and Respond to Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19) (<em>updated March 12, 2020)</em><br>
